title: Pushing Daisies Season 2
description:
Hey everyone! Couldn't find a torrent with all of Pushing Daisies season 2, so I downloaded the episodes individually and put them together.

These are all HD TV rips (although not mine), and are great quality. There are 10 episodes out, but the full season will eventually be 13 episodes. The last 3 are scheduled to air in summer 2009, which is too long to wait for a single Season 2 torrent in my opinion!
